DARBY
v.
CAMPBELL, et al. No. 171P15-2. Supreme Court of North Carolina. Sept. 24, 2015. Arthur Donald Darby, Jr., Fayetteville, for Darby, Arthur Donald (Jr.).

Opinion

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 17th of September 2015 by Plaintiff For Error Coram Nobis:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 24th of September 2015."
